  "texts": [
    "The plots can explain purchase patterns and the popularity of these products (due to the y-axis count), it can be deduced that holidays impact the behavior of Amazon customers.",
    "In the home entertainment category, it can be noticed that the activity increases around Christmas and new year times (December-January).",
    "This information can help in fake reviews detection, for instance to focus on the time periods of high activity where deceptive reviewers might belong.",
    "Since this study's focus is the review word count.",
    "Each category is analyzed by number of rows, minimum maximum and average word count, the start and end date for when the data was input, or categories existed."
  ]
}